{"sn1.17:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.17 ","sn1.17:0.2":"2. Nandanavagga ","sn1.17:0.3":"Dukkarasutta ","sn1.17:1.1":"“Dukkaram duttitikkhanca, ","sn1.17:1.2":"abyattena ca samannam; ","sn1.17:1.3":"Bahuhi tattha sambadha, ","sn1.17:1.4":"yattha balo visidati”ti. ","sn1.17:2.1":"“Katiham careyya samannam, ","sn1.17:2.2":"cittance na nivaraye; ","sn1.17:2.3":"Pade pade visideyya, ","sn1.17:2.4":"sankappanam vasanugoti. ","sn1.17:3.1":"Kummova angani sake kapale, ","sn1.17:3.2":"Samodaham bhikkhu manovitakke; ","sn1.17:3.3":"Anissito annamahethayano, ","sn1.17:3.4":"Parinibbuto nupavadeyya kanci”ti. "}